<L>__{interior his police car}
<A>__{he is behind her at a distance on a hilly mill valley road little streets, terraced hillsides, sharp turns. he goes slowly, looks around, thinks he's lost her. and then he sees the black ferrari parked in front of a house obscured by hedges. he parks the car a distance behind the ferrari, sits there a long beat. he gets out, goes carefully up to the hedges, looks. a small, nondescript house. he watches. he can't see anything inside the house. a beat, he reaches over to the mailbox and opens it. he takes an envelope out, looks at the name hazel dobkins.}
